	Many types of rotating equipment require shaft alignment. Misalignment of shafts can damage bearings, couplings and other machine components. This 2-minute, 46-second video explains the basics of shaft alignment, including the two forms of misalignment, how to correct misalignment, and the challenges of precision alignment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
